{
  "id": "019d286a-f2d7-7750-81b8-32e467cb26b8",
  "content": "## Core Types\n## RagPipeline\n\n### Factory function\n\n```rust\npub fn create_rag_pipeline(\n    store: Arc<dyn QueryableStore>,\n    engine: Arc<dyn InferenceEngine>,\n    graph: Option<Arc<dyn GraphStore>>,\n    generator: Option<Arc<dyn GenerationEngine>>,\n    config: &CorviaConfig,\n) -> RagPipeline {\n    let retriever: Arc<dyn Retriever> = match graph {\n        Some(g) => Arc::new(GraphExpandRetriever::new(store.clone(), engine.clone(), g)),\n        None => Arc::new(VectorRetriever::new(store.clone(), engine.clone())),\n    };\n    let augmenter = Arc::new(StructuredAugmenter::new(config));\n    RagPipeline::new(retriever, augmenter, generator, config.rag.clone())\n}\n```\n\nAuto-selects `GraphExpandRetriever` when `GraphStore` is available, falls back to `VectorRetriever`.\n",
  "source_version": "docs/rfcs/2026-03-02-m3.2-rag-pipeline-design.md",
